      <td>This release introduces a new family of VM instances that are optimized for consistent, high-compute workloads and offer a more than 40% performance improvement when compared to current GCP VMs. Using Second Generation Intel Xeon Scalable processors, C2 VMs can run at a sustained clock speed of 3.8 GHz. <a href="https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AFnwnKU4zqO57FqxT-M6ALoYBn72i9ooFegdr_8Zc27U6QfoxkclLwJ8zRV4Qi7hoEVVgqP2gXXvyWMKjCyUYvwUDe3SNYJPAz82fsJauruHvCqY5YZr_mLGsmnzbOA_7zVEeArsnQHFA0RqKRQqds6qzwr3LI_AT9Zf_TOF_RHu9g8w6ZT-Mw_F1At95rp-2sfPocGSRuph0JUuQJz8nxNRuHGNvxGLOD5ybhnXXtYJGKmiictFMqn1Y09zD2sSyJTBL6pM09v8NfrTD7n2qFW2tgnaK8gUtBSQoWzYTdmFwaVaOs7bm-HHyWmnj_fYnwo-tPcQ7JfZAak7fE7T6QQEmelxypp2rBbWaeCSJrgK6ZItaR7J9P4twWqS0STY1KQt210f8JEQq57yBD98tIwVWkN8Qc1dZ2u0dskkVpxIQy_dULqgChgyFQYDUYzgRf7kZu3icYfVCe06Ou_zwxe6zv1iG5RuAjJW7aY6Gi4I7URjDCGVMWRuAePRcT7Z22su6yDDfGITiYSHkw2ajs81K6A02nHfABcTQaV7S5f0oMJoXomIPw6croaD-blqpHra13plFso4ZizgP0I">Blog</a>
  </td>
   </tr>
</table>
<table>
   <tr>
      <td>Compute Engine – Memory-Optimized (M2) VMs: alpha</td>
   </tr>
</table>
<table>
<tr>
      <td>M2 VMs offer the highest memory configuration for a Compute Engine VM. They’re ideal for memory-intensive workloads like large in-memory databases and in-memory data analytics workloads. Our newest additions offer up to 12 TB of memory and 416 vCPUs. <a href="https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AFnwnKU4zqO57FqxT-M6ALoYBn72i9ooFegdr_8Zc27U6QfoxkclLwJ8zRV4Qi7hoEVVgqP2gXXvyWMKjCyUYvwUDe3SNYJPAz82fsJauruHvCqY5YZr_mLGsmnzbOA_7zVEeArsnQHFA0RqKRQqds6qzwr3LI_AT9Zf_TOF_RHu9g8w6ZT-Mw_F1At95rp-2sfPocGSRuph0JUuQJz8nxNRuHGNvxGLOD5ybhnXXtYJGKmiictFMqn1Y09zD2sSyJTBL6pM09v8NfrTD7n2qFW2tgnaK8gUtBSQoWzYTdmFwaVaOs7bm-HHyWmnj_fYnwo-tPcQ7JfZAak7fE7T6QQEmelxypp2rBbWaeCSJrgK6ZItaR7J9P4twWqS0STY1KQt210f8JEQq57yBD98tIwVWkN8Qc1dZ2u0dskkVpxIQy_dULqgChgyFQYDUYzgRf7kZu3icYfVCe06Ou_zwxe6zv1iG5RuAjJW7aY6Gi4I7URjDCGVMWRuAePRcT7Z22su6yDDfGITiYSHkw2ajs81K6A02nHfABcTQaV7S5f0oMJoXomIPw6croaD-blqpHra13plFso4ZizgP0I">Blog</a>
  </td>
   </tr>
</table>
<table>
   <tr>
      <td>Cloud Run: beta</td>
   </tr>
</table>
<table>
<tr>
      <td>Cloud Run brings serverless to containers, abstracting away all infrastructure management so that you can focus on building applications. Now you can run stateless HTTP containers in a fully managed environment or in your Kubernetes Engine cluster. <span><br /></span><a href="https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AFnwnKWCIzt8LNcDMMl1gWCfinNGSgO2dS2WqqHoCGXCZrmAoTVQRl9mcMRr8d7vp0ZQiQD6qED0DbSjnh-OlAnhdGDyLVe_ZkTWhreEDpE86Dwf5m1A6MyrKqoEUbRGzFYQtn9HeEwW-JzzxUP6SxFeGFUn4NX2SClrkSG5sqt-6W0ifYggp0A0OS4AS95ngFgibvAptFHz1KElVvCdlKHpZpbutI-B-4BYCdCnIZ1ke98hylp6i7URe2F8u7lv_dVFGGFs2uavplVYTyqQSht6ouY5LaUF77OU3iknNep0_IlEXqSSwkU5oy7BY7WIJ-ybcbkibl50oCGAvnjaus0nvPpnItLS3xQTJg">Product page</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AFnwnKVBAiMfmVo6oNRkCifN6L18JrXWPys_uel8NvTA94sQxxFNAakQA2mu9INnEvI6LTrim5b-uU6muS61TreHBiWcLHZ7Doc9KsHLSi_lBgqnnTrnOdsKx6BQ99iq1GsF0ulrvKKKEppZKrsfTgZgfZv5fnhA8CsnxLHurfj4sW9PY5qoKgDYpxieJ-Cso9YUEIGcbLJaPRzNnx56jR0VzH1ly7vV0bvDUvPmMGKkODMVZq-KzUMzuuDHsPzhYg_kfcR_KRTATtQKC79Sre_56bAp4lBE1CDl9j1lS2jxKtEWsAG-MFSCUK84-6zkiAgoHy1pUofAaIQ96srdmTMT8p0Vr1xKK43y2-TJ_QUt6-qRBPxD7xaS8hMDzbsjGue-FyjVWZ4vu8BZU1QABH297CtX-EnCbFQ7mEMeCuVrUJ-KUK0WuIjxd9ZSH6KTS00pRFnvS29g-v6fH8AD1NVoY0f5unKcQm8j2orD0D1a7LKZ33BQZvj1RwUpN8GFCpGmBhU9P-iubVGN3KRUF30m1voStlVO91hHwJAK-2dTDcBLb5gNMU6crqi9AhwAVtPPMzVI8RvV2CbbDGsgckYmByI">Blog</a>
  </td>
   </tr>
</table>
<table>
   <tr>
      <td>Compute Engine – explicit locality for snapshots: GA</td>
   </tr>
</table>
<table>
<tr>
      <td>Now customers have the ability to control data locality when creating snapshots of zonal or regional persistent disks. To store snapshots, customers can choose a multi-regional Cloud Storage bucket – available in the US, Europe, and Asia – or a specific Cloud Storage region. <a href="https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AFnwnKXT2bsXtWuHu-4F-9bEVzHeS3WSuI8kbQ3UaClY7HMaM0ZD8fKCZOLNtQFGU-8l1UmgQlDk0iRlJwIsyJHvOOiuE2myADmD3X49tDNMWbPDvTgAf5AWvMmEtRDTcpOZVsNmkHSJEpFFOIrOMKHx1t0oa-BySTibDFEaQSbAdYjQg5hahRPhm3Y0FyVfd7p1yHoVTFCvfGIK-S1hfOXULpFAwyrGOCcREjAYrJc6BUIyaZ5J2ckASczLntcJknn-jkMNwqPNC6B2gyHptC6JG9i5DGvOA8Rdtew3ALtXO5KQeQpqbcw_BF8opiwXD7QqXwgn3v27L5x5V-LqbebSs2cnr55AiHx3h5d_cPuZKXV0-XxHFpH_vdtnwriMVMxyHgcEDUvNvzpbwzcwDDX7vsWqPQkBwEnqKoWjByvStlfBVEOD7RPFDQQ">Documentation</a>
  </td>
   </tr>
</table>

