      <td>This latest BOSH release makes it simple to install, manage, and maintain Apigee Edge for Private Cloud 4.19.01. One of the key new features is the new Apigee Edge experience and OpenAPI Specification v3 support. <a href="https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AFnwnKVl26wWPEuPaeS6eFe31-HclOGNmR2Cb0sQfw86ZW4tcGYC5WcZXDPeSLORkHilxZ6Zh2WQsGPU73I8s-1J355vxqNihdYrpkljQln8O5BPSrAKRXqt_sw311IdkEx5_TiJTCQCV2HNOPcJe5x3NI3vFS8mUJsisLPRoNjs1324XwOGsJyM7ESAXH4Eaq2ypvoa">Documentation</a>
